---
title: block_creation (EIP-7934)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init
    q_init --> q_build : validator constructs candidate block
    q_build --> q_encode : encoded_size = len(rlp.encode(block))
    q_encode --> q_check : compare encoded_size to MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
    q_check --> q_propose : encoded_size <= MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
    q_check --> q_reduce : encoded_size > MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
    q_reduce --> q_build : remove transactions to reduce block size
    q_propose --> q_final : propose block to network
    q_final --> [*]

    note right of q_check
        INV-004: Block creation loop must terminate (transactions are finite)
        INV-005: Proposed block always satisfies encoded_size <= MAX_RLP_BLOCK_SIZE
        INV-006: Size check applies independently of gas-related metrics
    end note
